OL,5, New rules over which homes can be      
OL,6, forcibly switched to a prepayment meter
OL,7, have been criticised by campaigners who
OL,8, want a total ban.                      
OL,10,FCustomers must be given more chance to 
OL,11,Fclear debts and forced meter           
OL,12,Finstallations will be banned in homes  
OL,13,Fof those over 85, regulator Ofgem said.
OL,15,FCharities say the measures do not go   
OL,16,Ffar enough because they are voluntary -
OL,17,Fa claim rejected by Ofgem.             
OL,19,FFitting was halted after agents broke  
OL,20,Finto the homes of vulnerable people.   
